        },
        "text": "To ask a male \"What do you do every day?\", you say: \"بتعمل إيه كل يوم؟\" (bteʿmel ēh kull yōm?). Notice the 'ت' prefix and the masculine form of the verb.",
        "examples": [
          {
            "arabic": "بتعمل إيه كل يوم؟",
            "english": "What do you do every day? (to a male)",
            "transliteration": "Bteʿmel ēh kull yōm?"
          }
        ]
      }
